This application manages todos (CRUD operations).

It is using Spring MVC, Spring Security, JPA - Hibernate, Maven, JSTL.


To use it, open your favorite IDEA (mine is IntelliJ).
Wait for a while untill all dependencies are downloaded.

To login at http://localhost:8080/login, you can go to /src/main/java/com/wiqrug/MyFirstWebApp/security/SpringSecurityConfiguration.java class and find all the users and passwords.

h2 database is available at http://localhost:8080/h2-console


